transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Hanji.
Executive: Han mai bol raha hu madam Chaitanya Enterprises se.
Customer: Kahan se?
Executive: Solapur se Chaitanya Enterprises. Ji ji ji sir bataiye aap.
Customer: Haan. Maine aapko ek whatsapp kiya tha kal aapko phone bhi kiya tha aapne phone nahi kiya.
Executive: Ek second mai dekhti hu.
Customer: Delete kar do acha aapka kal aaya tha message mere ko na.
Customer: Haan kyuki wo pata nahi kon sa customer hai ye delete.
Executive: Sir ye na hamare side se delete nahi hoga. Ye aapke side se customers ko baat karke hatwana padega. So aap isko na batao.
Customer: Nahi nahi nahi nahi last time ek baar meri baat hui thi aapse aapne bola ki 30 day ke andar hai to hum karwa sakte hai.
Executive: Nahi nahi hum tab kara sakte hai jab customer nahi hata raha hai. Thik hai?
Customer: Wo customer wo nahi hai wo pata nahi kon sa customer hai pata bhi nahi phone bhi nahi utha raha hai mera.
Executive: Phone nahi utha raha?
Customer: Haan. Kyuki wo log bhi bina buyer se baat ki nahi to aap ek kaam karo aap mujhe customer ka ek baar contact do.
Customer: Contact nahi hai jo jo rating rating dala hai na mai aise hi send karke aapko print kar diya hai.
Executive: Haan usi customer jisne rating dali hai usi ka number chahiye mujhe.
Customer: Aapko nahi dikh sakta kya wo?
Executive: Nahi sir aapka personal data hum nahi de sakte na. To ye to aapka personal data ho gaya jin customers se aapki baat hui hai. To yahi sab cheeze hai.
Customer: Meri baat nahi hui phone nahi uthaya wo wo unknown customer hai pura.
Executive: Unknown customer hai?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Ek baar share kijiye mai try karti hu kyuki bina discussion kiye na sir nahi hatega wo.
Customer: Nahi karo karo discussion nahi mai dekho aapne last time bola tha kuch hai to hum help karenge isi vajah se maine aapko call kiya madam.
Executive: Nahi hum matlab ki hamari backend team karti hai to unke unko na thoda sa details chahiye hota hai isliye mai bol rahi hu. To agar ho to mujhe karta hu mai kyuki mai ek customer unknown hai aise hi online dal ke unhone dal diya hai rating kuch pata bhi nahi mujhe aisa hai.
Customer: Hmm hmm. Unknown customer hai wo abhi wo number kahan kitne din ka hai wo bhi number bahut purana number hai wo wo kaise check karu abhi online me jaake wo samajh nahi aa raha mujhe.
Executive: Accha wo kahan se check karna hai aap profile me jaiye. Catalog open karenge profile me jaiyega.
Customer: Ek minute ruko.
Executive: Login karna padega mujhe.
Customer: Ram babu.
Customer: Hmm ab open kiya abhi kis mein jao?
Executive: Hello. Haan abhi aapne open kiya na profile me jaiye. Profile me se ja kar ke third fourth number pe review and rating aa raha hoga.
Customer: Ek minute. Profile mein hai na?
Executive: Ji. To profile mein to rating kahan dikha raha hai?
Customer: Phone mein open kiya aapne?
Customer: Phone pe nahi system pe.
Executive: System pe open kiya na? Profile mein jab jayenge na to waha pe first primary detail second additional detail third website and fourth aapka rating and review.
Customer: Rating. Okay haan. Haan us pe click kariye waha pe search kijiye kon kon se customer hai. Haan ya ram babu hai idhar. Ram babu hai na is pe click karenge jab na reply ka ya aise kuch option aayega mere paas to nahi aa raha ya ram babu uske naam pe click kariye to wo lead manager me seedha lekar jayega aapko. Thik hai iska number aapko send karu kya? Haan ek baar number mujhe bhej do ya fir aap call karke unko bol do thoda politely ki sir aapka na nahi karegi madam wo kaisa rehta hai koi bhi online mai aapko send kar deta hu na aap ek baar ek kar lo. Haan aap mujhe bhejiye mai dekhti hu kyuki review and rating na sir to bahut rare case me hatate hai jaldi hatate nahi hai. Kyuki wo kya hota hai ki buyer aur supplier ka discussion hota hai.
Customer: Hmm hmm. Ye lekin ye unknown hi hai na customer mere liye. Koi nahi aap mujhe bhejo mai baat karke try karti hu khud se hatwane ka na.
Customer: Haan haan.
summary:
Concerns:

- Wants to remove a rating from an unknown customer.

- Unable to locate customer details in profile.



Resolution:

- Executive provided steps to find ratings in profile.

- Customer agreed to send the customer's number to executive.



Next Steps: 

- Executive will try to contact customer to remove rating.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Angry -> Satisfied



@@@Key Topics:

- rating, profile, customer, review
